Text.string: I, I can't even believe what I'm seeing right now.
What kinda... crazy crap is that?
Kinda feels like I should burp every once in a while!
Oh, sure, you think you can just -- you can just shoot me?!
Yeah! Get a load of that -- of all that science!
Get a -- get a load of these guys, huh?
You're gonna come down with a terminal case of my foot up your ass!
Terrible, you're just -- you're just the worst!
Hey. Hey! I need a new Warty.
W-W-Warty! I need a drink, Warty.
C-c-come on, Warty. We got work to do.
Get out here and HELP ME, Warty!
Not how I -- how I saw this going...
